39
00:01:56,920 --> 00:02:01,070
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">All right. Let's hear this
reason or whatever, then.</font>

40
00:02:01,070 --> 00:02:02,850
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">– I'll pass.
– H-Hey!</font>

41
00:02:02,850 --> 00:02:05,200
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I don't care about her past.</font>

42
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:07,520
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Where are you going, Luffy?</font>

43
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:07,540
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37" color="#d6d6d6">For a walk.</font>

44
00:02:07,540 --> 00:02:10,880
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">A-A walk?! You're not
gonna listen to this?!</font>

45
00:02:10,880 --> 00:02:12,260
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">No. I'll pass.</font>

46
00:02:13,610 --> 00:02:14,780
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Who's he?</font>

47
00:02:15,550 --> 00:02:18,250
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Don't mind him.
That's just how he is.</font>

48
00:02:18,250 --> 00:02:20,220
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">We'll hear you out.</font>

49
00:02:20,220 --> 00:02:23,740
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Though I don't think it's 
gonna change anything.</font>

50
00:02:23,740 --> 00:02:25,860
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Yeah! I'll listen, too!</font>

51
00:02:25,860 --> 00:02:29,710
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I wanna know what's
happening on this island!</font>

52
00:02:29,710 --> 00:02:32,680
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Me, too! I want to know
everything about Nami!</font>

53
00:02:34,590 --> 00:02:35,770
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">And now he's sleeping.</font>

54
00:02:35,770 --> 00:02:37,800
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Don't go to sleep right after you say that!</font>

55
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:45,850
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I see. This is why Nami
had such a hard time.</font>

56
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:53,290
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I fell asleep?</font>

57
00:02:53,290 --> 00:02:55,680
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Huh? Nojiko?</font>

58
00:02:57,270 --> 00:03:00,070
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Where could she have gone?</font>

59
00:03:05,210 --> 00:03:08,750
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Just a little longer, Bell-mère.</font>

60
00:03:09,710 --> 00:03:13,250
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Just a little longer, and everything 
will return to normal!</font>

61
00:03:13,250 --> 00:03:14,220
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Cocoyashi Village,</font>

62
00:03:14,220 --> 00:03:17,780
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">the tangerine orchard,
and even my dream!</font>

63
00:03:24,490 --> 00:03:28,020
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">It took eight years.</font>

64
00:03:38,070 --> 00:03:39,030
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">All done.</font>

65
00:03:39,030 --> 00:03:41,070
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">All done!</font>

66
00:03:44,470 --> 00:03:48,910
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Damn it, Nami! Not again!</font>

67
00:03:48,910 --> 00:03:51,180
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Let go!</font>

68
00:03:48,910 --> 00:03:51,180
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37" color="#d6d6d6">Oh? Did it again, Nacchan?</font>

69
00:03:51,180 --> 00:03:54,680
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I'm not a cat!</font>

70
00:03:51,180 --> 00:03:54,680
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37" color="#d6d6d6">You just never learn!</font>

71
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:55,780
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">You idiot!</font>

72
00:03:55,780 --> 00:03:58,720
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">How many times do I have to
tell you stealing is wrong?!</font>

73
00:03:59,750 --> 00:04:03,160
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">It's not my fault we're poor! </font>

74
00:04:03,690 --> 00:04:05,680
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">You meanie!</font>

75
00:04:06,390 --> 00:04:08,180
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Bell-mère!</font>

76
00:04:08,180 --> 00:04:13,200
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Bell-mère! Your no-good
cat's been at it again!</font>

77
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:18,260
<font face="Roboto" size="26"><font size="25"><font color="#000000">Bell-mère
<font size="23">Nami's and Nojiko's
Foster Mother</font></font></font></font>

78
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:18,260
<font face="Roboto" size="26"><font size="25">Bell-mère
<font size="23">Nami's and Nojiko's
Foster Mother</font></font></font>

79
00:04:15,870 --> 00:04:18,600
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Whadya want? You're so annoying!</font>

80
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:20,940
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Oh! Welcome home, Nami!</font>

81
00:04:20,940 --> 00:04:22,240
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I'm back!</font>

82
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:24,940
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Look! This is the umpteenth time!</font>

83
00:04:24,940 --> 00:04:26,910
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">She's infamous throughout the village now!</font>

84
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:29,850
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">So?</font>

85
00:04:29,850 --> 00:04:33,120
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Surely even you've
shoplifted before, Gen?</font>

86
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:35,460
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">You're why she acts this way!</font>

87
00:04:35,460 --> 00:04:36,990
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I'm just kidding!</font>

88
00:04:36,990 --> 00:04:42,300
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">All right. You paid for her, right?</font>

89
00:04:40,340 --> 00:04:42,300
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37" color="#d6d6d6">B-Bell-mère...</font>

90
00:04:42,300 --> 00:04:45,360
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Thanks so much.
I don't have money right now.</font>

91
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:47,260
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I'll pay you later...</font>

92
00:04:47,260 --> 00:04:50,060
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">with my body.</font>

93
00:04:51,020 --> 00:04:55,690
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Th-That's not wh-what I meant!</font>

94
00:04:55,690 --> 00:04:58,210
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Look at you blush!</font>

95
00:05:03,050 --> 00:05:06,110
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Oh? And why are you laughing?</font>

96
00:05:08,280 --> 00:05:11,820
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Try that again, and you'll 
get 100 spankings!</font>

97
00:05:11,820 --> 00:05:13,560
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I'm sorry!</font>

98
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:17,030
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">But I really wanted this book!</font>

99
00:05:17,030 --> 00:05:20,380
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">If you wanted it,
why didn't you just tell me?</font>

100
00:05:21,430 --> 00:05:23,640
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Because you wouldn't
buy it for me anyway.</font>

101
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:25,240
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Of course I would!</font>

102
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:27,370
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">We do have some
money stashed away.</font>

103
00:05:27,370 --> 00:05:31,110
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">But the villagers said the weather's 
been so good lately,</font>

104
00:05:31,110 --> 00:05:34,010
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">any old field will grow tons of tangerines.</font>

105
00:05:34,010 --> 00:05:37,420
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">We can't get a good price for ours, 
and they won't sell anyway.</font>

106
00:05:37,420 --> 00:05:39,650
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">They can mind their own business!</font>

107
00:05:39,650 --> 00:05:41,890
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">You're so dumb, Nami!</font>

108
00:05:41,890 --> 00:05:44,860
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I would've stolen it way better!</font>

109
00:05:45,890 --> 00:05:48,320
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I said no stealing!</font>

110
00:05:48,320 --> 00:05:51,060
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I was just joking!</font>

111
00:05:51,060 --> 00:05:52,800
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">That hurts!</font>

112
00:05:57,190 --> 00:06:00,020
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">But you know,
there's one thing for sure!</font>

113
00:06:00,020 --> 00:06:03,120
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">The maps you draw are
really amazing, Nami!</font>

114
00:06:04,190 --> 00:06:08,470
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">First you learned how to draw
sea charts, and now land maps!</font>

115
00:06:08,470 --> 00:06:11,540
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">This is a map of this island, isn't it?!</font>

116
00:06:12,350 --> 00:06:16,520
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">No one would ever think
such a little kid drew this!</font>

117
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:21,520
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I've been studying navigation, too!</font>

118
00:06:21,520 --> 00:06:23,630
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Even navigation?!</font>

119
00:06:23,630 --> 00:06:25,480
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">That's Nami's dream, right! </font>

120
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:26,920
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Yeah!</font>

121
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:31,520
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I'm gonna use my navigation skills
to sail all the world's seas!</font>

122
00:06:31,520 --> 00:06:35,790
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">And then I'm gonna make 
a world map of everything I see!</font>

123
00:06:36,510 --> 00:06:41,060
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">So your map of this island is your
first step toward your goal, then?</font>

124
00:06:41,850 --> 00:06:43,160
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Yeah!</font>

125
00:06:43,620 --> 00:06:45,920
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">A world map, huh?</font>

126
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:50,620
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Nami! Someday, you will make
your dream come true!</font>

127
00:06:53,230 --> 00:06:55,200
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I just know it!</font>

128
00:06:59,980 --> 00:07:02,440
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Hey, Bell-mère.</font>

129
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:04,730
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">You haven't been eating lately.</font>

130
00:07:04,730 --> 00:07:09,130
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I've been eating tangerines,
though. I'm on a diet!</font>

131
00:07:09,130 --> 00:07:10,990
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I don't need any food, either.</font>

132
00:07:10,990 --> 00:07:13,080
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Since when are you 
watching your figure?</font>

133
00:07:13,080 --> 00:07:15,250
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Kids need to eat right!</font>

134
00:07:15,250 --> 00:07:16,750
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">You keep lying!</font>

135
00:07:16,750 --> 00:07:21,020
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">You don't have any food because
we don't have any money!</font>

136
00:07:21,020 --> 00:07:21,900
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">For real?!</font>

137
00:07:21,900 --> 00:07:24,750
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">You're suffering so that we can–</font>

138
00:07:23,490 --> 00:07:24,750
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37" color="#d6d6d6">Diet!</font>

139
00:07:24,750 --> 00:07:29,000
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">You shouldn't underestimate
the rejuvenating power of tangerines!</font>

140
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:34,760
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">They're the reason I still have such 
glowing skin at the age of 30!</font>

141
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:36,500
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">But your hands are yellow.</font>

142
00:07:36,500 --> 00:07:38,440
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Just shut up and eat!</font>

143
00:07:40,270 --> 00:07:42,280
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Here you are, Nami! All done!</font>

144
00:07:42,280 --> 00:07:44,940
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">It's Bell-mère's own
<i>haute couture</i> brand!</font>

145
00:07:44,940 --> 00:07:47,020
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Another hand-me-down
from Nojiko?</font>

146
00:07:47,020 --> 00:07:50,750
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Don't worry about it!
It looks great on you, Nami!</font>

147
00:07:50,750 --> 00:07:52,750
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">This lion used to be a sunflower!</font>

148
00:07:52,750 --> 00:07:54,490
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">That's just how it is!</font>

149
00:07:54,490 --> 00:07:57,370
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">You're two years younger
than me, you know!</font>

150
00:07:57,370 --> 00:08:01,630
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Age has nothing to do with it!
I want new clothes, too!</font>

151
00:08:01,630 --> 00:08:03,760
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Mine are old clothes, too, you know!</font>

152
00:08:03,760 --> 00:08:07,500
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">You get my stuff 'cause
you're my baby sister!</font>

153
00:08:07,500 --> 00:08:10,240
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">But I'm not your real sister!</font>

154
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:13,500
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">We're not related by blood!</font>

155
00:08:13,500 --> 00:08:15,140
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Nami!</font>

156
00:08:22,520 --> 00:08:24,160
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Bell-mère!</font>

157
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:32,540
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">So what if you're not
related by blood?!</font>

158
00:08:35,540 --> 00:08:39,490
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Never say anything
stupid like that again!</font>

159
00:08:39,490 --> 00:08:41,880
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Wh-Whatever...</font>

160
00:08:41,880 --> 00:08:46,150
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">You're not our real mother, either!</font>

161
00:08:46,150 --> 00:08:49,710
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">You'd be better off without us,
wouldn't you?!</font>

162
00:08:50,410 --> 00:08:52,620
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">That way, you could eat,</font>

163
00:08:52,620 --> 00:08:56,390
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">buy all the clothes you want,
and be free!</font>

164
00:08:56,390 --> 00:08:58,230
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I wish...</font>

165
00:08:58,230 --> 00:09:02,350
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I wish someone richer
had adopted me instead!</font>

166
00:09:10,170 --> 00:09:12,180
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I-Is that so?</font>

167
00:09:13,170 --> 00:09:15,280
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Fine, then! Do whatever you want!</font>

168
00:09:15,280 --> 00:09:19,200
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">If you hate this house that much,
then go live somewhere else!</font>

169
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:21,950
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Stop it, you two!</font>

170
00:09:21,950 --> 00:09:24,000
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I will leave!</font>

171
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:26,090
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Nami!</font>

172
00:09:26,090 --> 00:09:27,890
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Nami!</font>

173
00:09:37,650 --> 00:09:39,430
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Bell-mère,</font>

174
00:09:39,430 --> 00:09:42,220
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">the three of us are a family!</font>

175
00:09:42,220 --> 00:09:44,770
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I'm sure Nami feels the same way!</font>

176
00:09:44,770 --> 00:09:47,120
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">She didn't mean what she said!</font>

177
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:51,250
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">You're very responsible, Nojiko.</font>

178
00:09:51,250 --> 00:09:53,980
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">That was real immature of me.</font>

179
00:09:54,450 --> 00:09:56,550
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Could you go bring Nami back for me?</font>

180
00:09:56,550 --> 00:09:59,550
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I'll have an amazing dinner 
ready before you get back!</font>

181
00:10:00,550 --> 00:10:01,780
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Okay!</font>

182
00:10:15,270 --> 00:10:17,470
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Okay, ma'am! How about this much?</font>

183
00:10:17,470 --> 00:10:20,720
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">What? Can't you do better than that?</font>

184
00:10:20,940 --> 00:10:23,600
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Right over here! 
Come see our low prices!</font>

185
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:28,770
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">You can't beat my fruit when it comes to freshness!</font>

186
00:10:36,890 --> 00:10:40,060
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">So, coming here from the outskirts
of the village is "running away"?</font>

187
00:10:40,060 --> 00:10:41,620
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">That sure is nice and convenient!</font>

188
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:45,790
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Here. Drink up before it gets cold!</font>

189
00:10:48,140 --> 00:10:52,040
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Bell-mère would be
happier if we were gone.</font>

190
00:10:52,660 --> 00:10:55,010
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Why do you think that?</font>

191
00:10:55,010 --> 00:10:58,050
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Having two children
costs lots of money,</font>

192
00:10:58,050 --> 00:11:02,150
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">and everyone in the village
hates her because of me.</font>

193
00:11:02,150 --> 00:11:05,480
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">You're old enough to consider 
others now, huh?</font>

194
00:11:06,700 --> 00:11:07,990
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Don't worry.</font>

195
00:11:07,990 --> 00:11:12,290
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">She was such a brat when she was your age, too.</font>

196
00:11:12,290 --> 00:11:13,770
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Bell-mère was?!</font>

197
00:11:13,770 --> 00:11:18,040
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Even now, she's still quite
a brat in the villagers' eyes!</font>

198
00:11:18,330 --> 00:11:22,000
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Everyone in the village was stunned when that brat suddenly said</font>

199
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:23,780
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">she was going to be a marine.</font>

200
00:11:23,780 --> 00:11:24,740
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">A marine?!</font>

201
00:11:24,740 --> 00:11:27,290
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Bell-mère was a marine?!</font>

202
00:11:27,290 --> 00:11:28,840
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Yeah.</font>

203
00:11:36,760 --> 00:11:41,520
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">"Pirates have to pay for
slaughtering innocent people!"</font>

204
00:11:41,520 --> 00:11:44,520
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">With those words,
she left the village.</font>

205
00:11:51,570 --> 00:11:56,040
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">She says she felt her time
to die had finally come.</font>

206
00:11:56,800 --> 00:12:00,470
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>Oh, well.</i></font>

207
00:12:18,590 --> 00:12:20,320
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>Is that your baby sister?</i></font>

208
00:12:24,930 --> 00:12:27,540
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>No. I don't know who she is.</i></font>

209
00:12:37,240 --> 00:12:39,480
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>You're still so innocent.</i></font>

210
00:12:54,300 --> 00:12:57,800
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">That was you, Nami.</font>

211
00:12:57,800 --> 00:13:03,220
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">When she saw you, Bell-mère
mustered up the will to live again.</font>

212
00:13:13,450 --> 00:13:15,620
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>It is a boat! I knew it!</i></font>

213
00:13:15,620 --> 00:13:18,810
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>On a stormy night like tonight?!
Who the hell could it be?!</i></font>

214
00:13:27,760 --> 00:13:30,620
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>Doctor! Call the doctor!</i></font>

215
00:13:31,030 --> 00:13:33,870
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>Bell-mère? Is that you, Bell-mère?!</i></font>

216
00:13:33,870 --> 00:13:36,420
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>– Bell-mère!
– What in the world happened?!</i></font>

217
00:13:39,870 --> 00:13:42,910
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>– These children! Whose...?!
– Doctor! They have terrible fevers!</i></font>

218
00:13:42,910 --> 00:13:45,260
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>They've been completely
worn out by the storm!</i></font>

219
00:13:45,260 --> 00:13:46,610
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>What?!</i></font>

220
00:13:48,580 --> 00:13:52,520
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>All right! But we need to tend to
those terrible wounds of yours, too!</i></font>

221
00:13:52,520 --> 00:13:54,460
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>Just hurry!</i></font>

222
00:13:54,460 --> 00:13:59,190
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>Please! Don't let them die!
Save them!</i></font>

223
00:13:59,190 --> 00:14:02,460
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>I beg of you!</i></font>

224
00:14:05,630 --> 00:14:09,070
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>What'd you just say, you troublemaker?! </i></font>

225
00:14:09,470 --> 00:14:13,330
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>I'm going to be their mother.
That's what I said.</i></font>

226
00:14:13,330 --> 00:14:14,410
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>You can't!</i></font>

227
00:14:14,410 --> 00:14:18,790
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>Don't do it! A punk like you
can't possibly raise children!</i></font>

228
00:14:18,790 --> 00:14:22,840
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>T-Take my advice! Give them
to a government institution!</i></font>

229
00:14:22,840 --> 00:14:24,460
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>I've already made up my mind!</i></font>

230
00:14:25,150 --> 00:14:27,490
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>I'm an adult now, too.</i></font>

231
00:14:27,490 --> 00:14:28,970
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>I was even in the Navy.</i></font>

232
00:14:28,970 --> 00:14:31,690
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>I think I'm a little more 
upstanding now.</i></font>

233
00:14:31,690 --> 00:14:35,630
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>I'm going to be responsible for taking care of these kids.</i></font>

234
00:14:35,630 --> 00:14:37,640
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>I'm going to raise them
to be wonderful people</i></font>

235
00:14:37,640 --> 00:14:40,940
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>who won't succumb to 
the world around them!</i></font>

236
00:14:40,940 --> 00:14:43,470
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>I'm going to live with these girls.</i></font>

237
00:14:43,470 --> 00:14:46,930
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>Nami and Nojiko saved my life.</i></font>

238
00:14:51,910 --> 00:14:56,750
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">You girls have a bond that goes
far deeper than a real family's.</font>

239
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:03,080
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Nami! I thought you'd be here!</font>

240
00:15:03,080 --> 00:15:04,840
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">N-Nojiko!</font>

241
00:15:04,840 --> 00:15:09,780
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Bell-mère is waiting for us!
She's making a yummy dinner!</font>

242
00:15:11,570 --> 00:15:12,760
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Okay!</font>

243
00:15:13,300 --> 00:15:17,000
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I bet it's your favorite!
Omelets with tangerine sauce!</font>

244
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:18,600
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Yes!</font>

245
00:15:19,180 --> 00:15:21,680
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Pirates, everyone!</font>

246
00:15:22,090 --> 00:15:25,300
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Pirates are coming!</font>

247
00:15:25,300 --> 00:15:28,990
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Pirates! Everyone hide!</font>

248
00:15:38,410 --> 00:15:40,610
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">– It's the Arlong Pirates!
– Arlong?!</font>

249
00:15:40,610 --> 00:15:42,110
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">That can't be!</font>

250
00:15:42,110 --> 00:15:44,850
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">What are fishmen from
the Grand Line doing here?!</font>

251
00:15:44,850 --> 00:15:48,630
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Was the rumor about a split 
in the Fishman Pirates true?</font>

252
00:15:48,630 --> 00:15:50,190
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Nami! Nojiko!</font>

253
00:15:50,190 --> 00:15:51,790
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Gen!</font>

254
00:15:51,790 --> 00:15:55,180
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">It's dangerous here!
Go hide in the woods!</font>

255
00:15:55,180 --> 00:15:56,680
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Huh? But...</font>

256
00:15:56,680 --> 00:15:58,260
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Go! Now!</font>

257
00:16:09,270 --> 00:16:12,860
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">You seem to be in excellent spirits, 
you pathetic humans!</font>

258
00:16:12,860 --> 00:16:15,150
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">As of this moment, this village–</font>

259
00:16:15,150 --> 00:16:18,450
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">no, this island is now
under my control!</font>

260
00:16:20,220 --> 00:16:21,820
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Listen up!</font>

261
00:16:21,820 --> 00:16:26,630
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">On this memorable day, 
you will all buy your lives from me!</font>

262
00:16:28,560 --> 00:16:33,130
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">100,000 belly per adult.
50,000 belly per kid.</font>

263
00:16:33,130 --> 00:16:35,430
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Those who can't pay... will die! </font>

264
00:16:37,500 --> 00:16:39,720
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">What do we do, Nojiko?</font>

265
00:16:40,470 --> 00:16:42,670
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">We can't pay that much!</font>

266
00:16:42,670 --> 00:16:44,780
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">But they might not spot our house!</font>

267
00:16:44,780 --> 00:16:47,190
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">You can't see it from the village!</font>

268
00:16:52,070 --> 00:16:54,280
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">How much did we get, brother?</font>

269
00:16:54,690 --> 00:16:57,240
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Just over 25 million, I'd say.</font>

270
00:16:57,590 --> 00:16:58,960
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Excellent!</font>

271
00:17:03,290 --> 00:17:06,200
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Sounds like we'll have to pay 100,000 belly per person</font>

272
00:17:06,200 --> 00:17:08,630
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">every month for the rest of our lives!</font>

273
00:17:08,630 --> 00:17:11,200
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">100,000?! We can't
make a living that way!</font>

274
00:17:11,200 --> 00:17:12,300
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Endure it for now!</font>

275
00:17:12,300 --> 00:17:15,930
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">We should just be glad no one 
in the village has died.</font>

276
00:17:15,930 --> 00:17:20,120
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">All right! Time to go, brothers!</font>

277
00:17:23,070 --> 00:17:26,190
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Arlong! There's smoke coming 
from outside the village!</font>

278
00:17:32,420 --> 00:17:33,900
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Okay!</font>

279
00:17:33,900 --> 00:17:35,620
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">All right, let's see!</font>

280
00:17:35,620 --> 00:17:37,220
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">That's too good!</font>

281
00:17:37,220 --> 00:17:39,620
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Nothing's quite like Bell-mère's
special tangerine sauce!</font>

282
00:17:39,620 --> 00:17:42,590
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Nami and Nojiko are gonna
leap out of their seats!</font>

283
00:17:42,590 --> 00:17:45,460
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">The smoke is coming from a house!</font>

284
00:17:46,460 --> 00:17:49,420
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Oh? We almost missed it.</font>

285
00:17:49,420 --> 00:17:50,880
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Damn!</font>

286
00:17:50,880 --> 00:17:52,370
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Bell-mère!</font>

287
00:17:53,250 --> 00:17:55,720
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Let's go! Let's collect our money!</font>

288
00:17:57,070 --> 00:17:59,810
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Whoa, this is bad! The pirates...</font>

289
00:17:59,810 --> 00:18:01,760
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">...are headed to Bell-mère's house!</font>

290
00:18:05,700 --> 00:18:08,190
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Hey! Nojiko and Nami are gone!</font>

291
00:18:08,190 --> 00:18:09,230
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">What?!</font>

292
00:18:09,750 --> 00:18:13,790
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Ten more minutes for the duck in
the oven. And the stew is boiling.</font>

293
00:18:13,790 --> 00:18:15,830
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">This'll be a big blow
to our family budget.</font>

294
00:18:15,830 --> 00:18:19,160
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">But I guess I'll splurge, anyway!</font>

295
00:18:25,770 --> 00:18:29,060
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Bell-mère's gonna...
Bell-mère's gonna...</font>

296
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:33,700
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Bell-mère's gonna be killed!</font>

297
00:18:40,590 --> 00:18:43,680
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">We can't just abandon Bell-mère!</font>

298
00:18:43,680 --> 00:18:47,430
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Damn! Why did this have to happen?!
Don't jump the gun, Bell-mère!</font>

299
00:18:49,040 --> 00:18:53,150
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Delicious! Nothing's quite like
my special tangerine sauce!</font>

300
00:18:53,150 --> 00:18:55,610
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Ten more minutes for
the duck in the oven.</font>

301
00:18:55,610 --> 00:18:57,780
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Got the side of vegetables,</font>

302
00:18:57,780 --> 00:18:59,580
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">and the stew is boiling.</font>

303
00:18:59,580 --> 00:19:02,160
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Now just some fried rice omelets,
and everything's ready!</font>

304
00:19:02,720 --> 00:19:05,520
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">This'll be a big blow
to our family budget.</font>

305
00:19:13,830 --> 00:19:15,750
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Oh, are they back?</font>

306
00:19:23,080 --> 00:19:26,640
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">It's open! Come on in!</font>

307
00:19:28,170 --> 00:19:29,640
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Pardon me.</font>

308
00:19:57,370 --> 00:20:00,920
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">You've got bad luck. I'm a former marine.</font>

309
00:20:01,370 --> 00:20:06,730
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">What brings Grand Line pirates all 
the way out to Cocoyashi Village?</font>

310
00:20:11,980 --> 00:20:12,990
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">What's so funny?!</font>

311
00:20:19,890 --> 00:20:24,390
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Weak! You're weak! So weak!</font>

312
00:20:24,390 --> 00:20:28,920
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Your inferior species is so powerless!</font>

313
00:20:35,990 --> 00:20:38,640
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Let's escape with her 
out the back door!</font>

314
00:20:38,640 --> 00:20:40,560
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">But the pirates might already be there!</font>

315
00:20:40,560 --> 00:20:41,410
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">We'll be fine!</font>

316
00:20:41,410 --> 00:20:42,640
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Hold it!</font>

317
00:20:46,580 --> 00:20:48,610
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">– Doctor!
– You mustn't return home!</font>

318
00:20:48,610 --> 00:20:49,150
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Wha...?!</font>

319
00:20:49,150 --> 00:20:51,370
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Move! We have to save Bell-mère!</font>

320
00:20:51,370 --> 00:20:53,290
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Nojiko! Nami!</font>

321
00:20:53,290 --> 00:20:55,350
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Listen closely, you two!</font>

322
00:20:55,350 --> 00:20:58,360
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">This isn't the time to–
Actually, this is the perfect time...</font>

323
00:20:58,360 --> 00:21:01,780
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I must tell you 
a somewhat cruel story!</font>

324
00:21:02,750 --> 00:21:03,950
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Doctor?</font>

325
00:21:06,090 --> 00:21:07,830
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Bell-mère!</font>

326
00:21:16,140 --> 00:21:20,450
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I can't do anything!
These guys are real monsters!</font>

327
00:21:20,450 --> 00:21:21,600
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I'm gonna be killed!</font>

328
00:21:21,600 --> 00:21:24,050
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Nojiko! Nami!</font>

329
00:21:24,050 --> 00:21:25,870
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Bell-mère!</font>

330
00:21:25,870 --> 00:21:28,730
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Don't waste your life for some
pathetic sense of justice!</font>

331
00:21:28,730 --> 00:21:30,260
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Some battles aren't worth fighting!</font>

332
00:21:30,260 --> 00:21:33,460
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Some issues can be solved with money!</font>

333
00:21:33,460 --> 00:21:35,300
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Gen...</font>

334
00:21:35,300 --> 00:21:38,130
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">That's right, marine girl.</font>

335
00:21:38,130 --> 00:21:41,330
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">100,000 per adult. 50,000 per kid.</font>

336
00:21:41,330 --> 00:21:43,570
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">If you can pay for your whole family,
I'll let you live.</font>

337
00:21:43,570 --> 00:21:45,400
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">You should be thankful I'm telling you.</font>

338
00:21:45,400 --> 00:21:46,860
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">My whole family?</font>

339
00:21:49,270 --> 00:21:53,540
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">That's 200,000 in total.
How much do you have, all together?</font>

340
00:21:54,410 --> 00:21:58,480
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Including what I've squirreled away...
a little over 100,000.</font>

341
00:21:59,750 --> 00:22:03,720
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Hey! There's a meal for 
three people in here!</font>

342
00:22:03,720 --> 00:22:07,320
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Oh? A family of three, huh?</font>

343
00:22:08,860 --> 00:22:11,320
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I almost forgot!</font>

344
00:22:12,660 --> 00:22:17,030
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">She invited me and my friend 
to dinner tonight!</font>

345
00:22:17,030 --> 00:22:20,510
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Come, Bell-mère.
Hurry and pay your amount.</font>

346
00:22:20,510 --> 00:22:22,970
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Our delicious food's going to get cold!</font>

347
00:22:22,970 --> 00:22:24,150
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Gen...</font>

348
00:22:24,150 --> 00:22:28,550
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I hear you have 100,000.
Thank goodness you have enough!</font>

349
00:22:28,550 --> 00:22:31,170
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Now everyone in the village is spared!</font>

350
00:22:31,170 --> 00:22:32,520
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">It's true.</font>

351
00:22:32,520 --> 00:22:37,060
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">The village register has no record 
of her getting married or giving birth.</font>

352
00:22:37,060 --> 00:22:38,890
