357
00:22:42,970 --> 00:22:44,520
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Do you understand?!</font>

358
00:22:44,520 --> 00:22:48,030
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">There's no proof that you two
and Bell-mère are family!</font>

359
00:22:48,030 --> 00:22:50,860
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Leave this island before
they take notice of you!</font>

360
00:22:50,860 --> 00:22:52,220
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Escape across the sea!</font>

361
00:22:53,300 --> 00:22:56,630
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">There's no other way for
all three of you to survive!</font>

362
00:22:56,630 --> 00:23:00,070
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I feel it's reckless to send you two
out to sea at such a young age!</font>

363
00:23:00,070 --> 00:23:02,210
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">There's a chance something 
bad could happen!</font>

364
00:23:02,210 --> 00:23:03,470
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">But at least you'll have–</font>

365
00:23:03,470 --> 00:23:04,200
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">No.</font>

366
00:23:05,540 --> 00:23:07,500
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I don't want to!</font>

367
00:23:07,500 --> 00:23:11,270
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I... want to live in this village.</font>

368
00:23:11,270 --> 00:23:12,610
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Is it because we're poor...</font>

369
00:23:12,610 --> 00:23:16,680
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">that I can't be Bell-mère's
daughter anymore?!</font>

370
00:23:16,680 --> 00:23:20,140
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Why? Why?!</font>

371
00:23:22,760 --> 00:23:26,380
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Thank goodness.
Now they won't kill anyone.</font>

372
00:23:26,740 --> 00:23:28,340
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">All right, we'll leave the village!</font>

373
00:23:27,960 --> 00:23:28,340
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37" color="#d6d6d6">Nojiko!</font>

374
00:23:28,340 --> 00:23:32,350
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Let's go! Because that means
Bell-mère gets to live!</font>

375
00:23:47,930 --> 00:23:49,080
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Hold it.</font>

376
00:23:49,080 --> 00:23:51,540
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Who said I paid for myself?</font>

377
00:23:52,500 --> 00:23:55,680
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">That 100,000 is for my two daughters.</font>

378
00:23:55,680 --> 00:23:57,200
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I don't have enough for myself!</font>

379
00:23:59,470 --> 00:24:00,760
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Bell-mère! What are you–</font>

380
00:24:00,760 --> 00:24:02,060
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I'm sorry, Gen.</font>

381
00:24:02,060 --> 00:24:05,430
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I just can't say
I don't have a family...</font>

382
00:24:05,430 --> 00:24:08,180
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">even... if it costs me my life.</font>

383
00:24:10,130 --> 00:24:11,270
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">How could she!</font>

384
00:24:11,270 --> 00:24:15,600
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Yeah, maybe we're not
related by blood,</font>

385
00:24:15,600 --> 00:24:17,740
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">but we're a family.</font>

386
00:24:17,740 --> 00:24:20,240
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I want to be their parent,
even if it's only in name.</font>

387
00:24:21,590 --> 00:24:24,780
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">They're... my kids.</font>

388
00:24:25,780 --> 00:24:28,410
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Bell-mère!</font>

389
00:24:26,540 --> 00:24:28,410
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37" color="#d6d6d6">Wait, you two!</font>

390
00:24:28,410 --> 00:24:32,630
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37"><i>I wish someone richer had 
adopted me instead!</i></font>

391
00:24:32,630 --> 00:24:36,120
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">It was just a lie! I was lying!</font>

392
00:24:36,120 --> 00:24:38,690
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Bell-mère!</font>

393
00:24:51,870 --> 00:24:57,380
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I wanted... to buy you lots
more books and clothes.</font>

394
00:24:57,380 --> 00:24:58,450
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I'm sorry!</font>

395
00:24:58,450 --> 00:25:01,420
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I was never able to be 
more of a mother to you!</font>

396
00:25:01,420 --> 00:25:02,480
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">That's not true!</font>

397
00:25:02,480 --> 00:25:04,250
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">We don't need anything!
Just don't die!</font>

398
00:25:04,250 --> 00:25:05,890
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Stay with us forever!</font>

399
00:25:05,890 --> 00:25:09,380
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I want you to see
the world map I draw!</font>

400
00:25:10,990 --> 00:25:13,530
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Yeah... your map...</font>

401
00:25:13,530 --> 00:25:17,710
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Make your dream... come true!</font>

402
00:25:19,030 --> 00:25:20,670
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Live!</font>

403
00:25:20,670 --> 00:25:23,500
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Bell-mère!</font>

404
00:25:25,140 --> 00:25:27,400
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">These're your girls, I take it?</font>

405
00:25:29,680 --> 00:25:31,950
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Yeah, that's right!</font>

406
00:25:31,950 --> 00:25:34,650
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Promise me you won't
lay a hand on them!</font>

407
00:25:34,650 --> 00:25:38,090
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Of course! As long as
you die like a good girl!</font>

408
00:25:38,090 --> 00:25:39,220
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Help us!</font>

409
00:25:51,630 --> 00:25:53,470
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Now they're thirsty for blood.</font>

410
00:25:53,470 --> 00:25:56,170
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Don't kill 'em. Just handle 
'em as you see fit.</font>

411
00:25:56,170 --> 00:26:00,460
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Perfect timing for our first 
example to the others!</font>

412
00:26:04,710 --> 00:26:06,550
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Now you die because of your worthless love.</font>

413
00:26:16,450 --> 00:26:18,440
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">Nojiko! Nami!</font>

414
00:26:21,620 --> 00:26:23,560
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="37">I love you!</font>

